            <title>Major Terran World Powers</title>

            <section>The Conservancy</section>

            <para>
            The Conservancy is both a set of Terran republics and the governing body
            that rules them. It is a quasi-mercantile organization funded by
            controlled tourism and payment for its Terraforming services.
            </para>

            <para>
            In land area it controls much of what is currently Mexico, Guatamala,
            all the way down to Peru and Brazil. 

            </para>

