            \chapter{Religious Organizations}

            \section{Wiccans}

            A semi-mystical coalition of churches derived from the pagan 
            movements of the 1990s, the Unitarian Universalist and Humanist 
            movements of the 2000s, and the New Bhudda movement of 2020.

            \section{Cestus Dei}

            A result of the ``Fire Reformation'' of the Catholic Church and
            vatican IIII, the Cestus Dei are a missionary organization derived 
            from the original Society of Jesus. As the name implies, the Cestus 
            Dei is a militant brotherhood/Sisterhood

